Package org.gicentre.treemappa.gui Description

Graphical User Interface classes for use with treeMappa.

This package includes classes for constructing the Graphical User Interface used by the TreeMappa application. Also includes a renderer plug-in capability to allow alternative renderers to be used with Processing.
